{"tid":1382484,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"係時候轉入地下抗爭活動！","createTime":"2019-07-29T13:16:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T16:59:26.000Z","uid":53577,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1bee05e49039a571c587e07207e3b00e719ab189","tid":1382484,"uid":53577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:16:10.000Z","msg":"先一部份人轉地下，以4人（或N人，deception煙幕）為1 unit, 每人以代號callsign 稱呼（例184A1)<br />\n<br />\n分工如下：<br />\n<br />\n1 情報收集，揾仔<br />\n<br />\n2 情報核實，控制中心<br />\n<br />\n3 行動支援，狗仔隊<br />\n<br />\n4 資源支援，lT ，hacker<br />\n<br />\n5 xxx<br />\n<br />\n所有參與者係Anonymous, 冇固定，彈出彈入"},{"pid":"4cbb88d06a025becc1d23ce8aa19f5c36886ee5c","tid":1382484,"uid":279145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:18:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d2c36570ea8805f68474bbabe1fc817f845e87ab","tid":1382484,"uid":273716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:20:23.000Z","msg":"眾籌"},{"pid":"f75f1c8ab3e994d615810ce77df7b5b65fbf32dd","tid":1382484,"uid":235580,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:22:23.000Z","msg":"全部手足同我推！ 如何令黑警有所顧忌有所恐懼！ 如何從狗屋內部分解黑警！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1378251\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1378251</a>"},{"pid":"86e46f8cb326cbf98a47a85083f3d0f23386619b","tid":1382484,"uid":53577,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:24:33.000Z","msg":"開頭可成立小形型行動群組（group of unit)， 例:<br />\n<br />\n4人情報小組（含資料搜集）<br />\n2人現場核實、睇水<br />\n1人行動<br />\n<br />\n這裡一共3組! 所有人可互相不認識，以callsign互動，任務完結即不再見，減低被破解機會 ."},{"pid":"37d38ecc0da19939b6d5a9bb0c7d419937b596b6","tid":1382484,"uid":53577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:27:52.000Z","msg":"呢種組織可無限擴大，甚至可能變成香港有幾千萬人參與各種小組，因為每人可以同時參與幾個小組，用不同分身所以係冇辦法破解个"},{"pid":"573706787be56399314875ef0b38e263693f0eb6","tid":1382484,"uid":53577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:28:55.000Z","msg":"大家可以推， 但係唔需要覆！<br />\n<br />\n因為呢種組織設計，就係Anonymous！保持機密！"},{"pid":"2eaab9cbeb114fbf763fc07ca32e518330b55790","tid":1382484,"uid":53577,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:30:30.000Z","msg":"以後香港人再唔係一個RFID<br />\n<br />\n而係無數分身 隨時轉換 冇辦法跟蹤"},{"pid":"8b5f48d9ecc7624296bbdad71e6f67bb993413c9","tid":1382484,"uid":53577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:31:23.000Z","msg":"呢種模式甚至可以發展到大陸！<br />\n大陸人自己參與，自己變身，效果不敢想像!"},{"pid":"5fda2f58e7f91e10125796163e03b7861765a3eb","tid":1382484,"uid":53577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:40:02.000Z","msg":"這是播下人類希望的種子，<br />\n犯法嘅事唔好做！<br />\n只做對香港有用嘅事!"},{"pid":"fbab9e9d1a6cc4f5d5767cfee2c849595b3b732c","tid":1382484,"uid":53577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:50:37.000Z","msg":"喺將來嘅 地下抗爭中<br />\n<br />\n反監控同埋通訊工具係最最重要<br />\n<br />\n將來好大機會係用最原始嘅方式通訊聯絡，其一就係遞紙仔同密碼，而need to know only 就係保護各組員最重要嘅方法!"},{"pid":"619f89087f769c294111223aa055cf9fa5a2d2de","tid":1382484,"uid":53577,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:53:36.000Z","msg":"從此以後絕對要注意喺網上一言一行！<br />\n因為呢一樣嘢會留低你哋嘅足跡，大數據同超級電腦可以根據你哋嘅足跡搵你哋出嚟！<br />\n<br />\n網上留言要小心，不能留下蹤跡以及把柄."},{"pid":"bd9a1362ceb2c8032461e77eddb3be480e5100da","tid":1382484,"uid":53577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:01:00.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"54a2ce10968da9aa178f2fd1408a00e7dd2f1d71","tid":1382484,"uid":53577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T17:06:51.000Z","msg":"pish<br />\n<br />\n送頭正on9, 零效益， 助長了對方氣燄， 其實係罪人."},{"pid":"bd2ccfe76ebd6e5880b25ee26b30c64c5874ae12","tid":1382484,"uid":53577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T01:56:57.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"72943f0c19e77575af858af3cc1e7b573732fc54","tid":1382484,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T01:57:24.000Z","msg":"忍者時代"},{"pid":"e